<li sourcefile="../../Documentation/CrossPlatform/LeapMotionMRTK.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Open the <strong sourcefile="../../Documentation/CrossPlatform/LeapMotionMRTK.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Input Data Providers</strong> section, select <strong sourcefile="../../Documentation/CrossPlatform/LeapMotionMRTK.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Add Data Provider</strong> at the top, a new data provider will be added at the end of the list.  Open the new data provider and set the <strong sourcefile="../../Documentation/CrossPlatform/LeapMotionMRTK.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Type</strong> to <strong sourcefile="../../Documentation/CrossPlatform/LeapMotionMRTK.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Microsoft.MixedReality.Toolkit.LeapMotion.Input &gt; LeapMotionDeviceManager</strong></li>
</ul>
<p sourcefile="../../Documentation/CrossPlatform/LeapMotionMRTK.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48"><img src="../Images/CrossPlatform/LeapMotion/LeapAddDataProvider.png" sourcefile="../../Documentation/CrossPlatform/LeapMotionMRTK.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48" alt="LeapAddDataProvider"></p>
